/trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-768x572.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-400x298.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-800x595.jpg 800w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero width="966" height="719" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image amp-wp-enforced-sizes" alt="TrueProfit vs BeProfit: Which Is The Ultimate #1 Profit-Tracking Solution? - TrueProfit" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png 966w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-300x223.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-768x572.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-400x298.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/TrueProfit-vs-BeProfit-trueprofit-thumbnail-blog-800x595.jpg 800w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img> </figure> <div class="amp-wp-article-content"> <div class="amp-wp-content the_content"> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Tired of tracking your sales data from 10+ different sources manually? And now you’re looking for a tracking solution to take the heavy lifting off your plate? Well, you’ve come to the right place.</p> <p>In this blog, we’ll dive into a <strong>head-to-head comparison</strong> between two leading players in the market: <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/trueprofit-vs-beprofit/" data-schema-attribute=""><strong>TrueProfit vs BeProfit</strong></a>. Both these apps have gained significant popularity among Shopify users, but which is truly worth your time and investment?</p> <p>Let’s explore!</p> <h2>TrueProfit vs BeProfit: A Quick Glance</h2> <p>Before we dive deeper into TrueProfit vs BeProfit comparison, let us help you have a better understanding of these top <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/profit-tracker-apps/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">Shopify profit tracker apps</a>.</p> <h3>What is TrueProfit?</h3> <p><a href="https://trueprofit.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">TrueProfit</a> has become popular among Shopify store owners, thanks to its powerful tracking capacities.</p> <p>TrueProfit is a profit calculator app that integrates and tracks all kinds of expenses from your Shopify stores, along with multiple integrated advertising platforms (<em>Facebook, Google, Bing, Snapchat, and TikTok</em>).</p> <p>The app is able to gather financial data from multiple sources to show you your accurate real-time profit, <strong>in one single unified dashboard</strong>! TrueProfit analyzes your profitability from various perspectives: product, customer, marketing channels, etc.</p> <h3><a href="https://shopify.pxf.io/daVP4K" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><amp-img data-hero class="aligncenter wp-image-3599 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1.png" alt="" width="500" height="250" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1.png 600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1-300x150.png 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1-400x200.png 400w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="aligncenter wp-image-3599 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="" width="500" height="250" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1.png 600w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1-300x150.png 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/shopify-free-trial-3-months-1-400x200.png 400w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img></a></h3> <p>In addition to tracking and analyzing real-time statistics, TrueProfit also automates the overall accounting process. Thanks to its capability to calculate advanced statistics and generate customizable reports, TrueProfit visualizes business performance and displays profits and losses.</p> <p>TrueProfit’s excellent features and automation is definitely what you need in making data-driven decisions to expand your business’s potential.</p> <figure id="attachment_3340" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3340 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-300x139.jpg" alt="TrueProfit provides real-time profit analytics for Shopify" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3340 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="TrueProfit provides real-time profit analytics for Shopify" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-trueprofit.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>TrueProfit automatically tracks and shows you your real-time revenues, profits &amp; losses</em></figcaption></figure> <h3>What is BeProfit?</h3> <p>BeProfit is famous for its real-time data-tracking solution that empowers merchants to stay on top of all their finances.</p> <p>As a reliable profit analytics app, BeProfit provides you with a clear and organized overview of your Shopify sales, expenses, and profits across multiple platforms. Overall business statistics tracking can be done within one convenient dashboard. You can easily track your revenue streams, analyze your profit margins, and identify key trends.</p> <figure id="attachment_3339" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3339 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-300x139.jpg" alt="BeProfit is a profit analytics app with extensive tracking features - trueprofit vs beprofit" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/what-is-beprofit-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://t