ure id="attachment_3333" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3333 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-300x141.jpg" alt="TrueProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store" width="1200" height="563" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-300x141.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-768x361.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1536x721.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-400x188.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-800x376.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1400x657.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3333 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="TrueProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store" width="1200" height="563" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-300x141.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1024x481.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-768x361.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1536x721.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-400x188.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-800x376.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing-1400x657.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-trueprofit-pricing.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>TrueProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store</em></figcaption></figure> <h4>BeProfit</h4> <p><strong>BeProfit has four pricing plans as well, with one free and three paid plans</strong>:</p> <ol> <li><strong>Starter Plan:</strong> BeProfit offers the Starter plan for free, accommodating up to 5 monthly orders;</li> <li><strong>Basic Plan:</strong> costs $25 monthly and includes the same features as the STARTER PLAN. However, it incurs an exceeding order fee of $0.3 per order above 200 monthly orders;</li> <li><strong>Pro Plan:</strong> priced at $75 per month, includes additional features like Custom reports, Customizable dashboards, P&amp;L reports, and Unlimited filters. It incurs an exceeding order fee of $0.2 per order above 600 monthly orders;</li> <li><strong>Ultimate Plan:</strong> is priced at $150 per month and includes Marketing insights, UTM attribution, LTV cohort analysis, and a Multi-shop dashboard. It incurs an exceeding order fee of $0.1 per order above 1,200 monthly.</li> </ol> <figure id="attachment_3332" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3332 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-300x136.jpg" alt="BeProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store" width="1200" height="545" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-300x136.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1024x465.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-768x349.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1536x698.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-400x182.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-800x363.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1400x636.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3332 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="BeProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store" width="1200" height="545" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-300x136.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1024x465.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-768x349.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1536x698.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-400x182.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-800x363.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing-1400x636.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/1-beprofit-pricing.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>BeProfit’s pricing plans on the Shopify App Store</em></figcaption></figure> <h4>Final verdict</h4> <table class="table table-hover acsseb0ee"> <tbody> <tr class="acss432ee"> <td class="acsse6f7c"><strong>TrueProfit wins.</strong> <p>Though <strong>BeProfit has one free plan, it’s limited</strong> because if you have more than five orders per month, you’ll have to move to the Basic plan at $25/month.</p> <p>And from there, TrueProfit’s pricing plans offer better value for your money because:</p> <ul> <li>At $25, TrueProfit allows 300 monthly orders and charges $0.2/exceeding order. Meanwhile, at $25, BeProfit limits only 200 monthly orders and charges you $0.3/exceeding order.</li> </ul> <ul> <li>Plus, TrueProfit has the maximum surcharge- this is extremely important if you have many orders.</li> </ul> <p class="acss2db15"><em>E.g:  if you have 10,000 monthly orders, the monthly fee you’ll have to pay for TrueProfit for its $25/month plan is $450. Meanwhile, this number with BeProfit is $3,250 for the same $25/month plan.</em></p> <ul> <li>TrueProfit has four paid plans, while BeProfit only has three paid ones. Hence, it’s safe to say that <strong>TrueProfit’s pricing plans offer merchants more flexible options</strong>.</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>#2. TrueProfit vs BeProfit: Features</h3> <h4>TrueProfit</h4> <p>TrueProfit has a lot of robust tracking features, allowing you to track not only your site-width profits and losses but the detailed breakdown of your store analytics:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Auto-track all kinds of costs:</strong> You can effortlessly track various costs associated with your business using TrueProfit. This includes COGS (Cost of Goods Sold), shipping costs, transaction fees, and customs costs. This comprehensive tracking ensures that you have a complete overview and full control of your expenses.</li> <li><strong>Real-time sync ad spends:</strong> Sync your ad spending data from multiple advertising platforms to one tracking platform, such as Facebook, Google, Bing, Snapchat, TikTok, and Amazon. In real time, you can analyze the effectiveness of your advertising campaigns and their impact on your overall profitability.</li> <li><strong>Profit tracker:</strong> Stay on top of your financial health with the <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/why-you-need-a-profit-tracking-app/#ftoc-heading-6" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">Profit and Loss (PnL) Report provided by TrueProfit</a>. This feature gives you a clear picture of your revenue, expenses, and profit margins. From there, it allows you to identify areas for improvement.</li> <li><strong>Product analytics:</strong> Gain valuable insights into your most profitable items and product bundles. TrueProfit’s product analytics feature helps you understand which products are driving the most revenue, allowing you to optimize your product offerings and maximize profits.</li> <li><strong>Know your <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/customer-lifetime-value/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">customer lifetime value</a>:</strong> Understand the lifetime value (LTV) of your customers, as well as metrics like customer <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/ltv-cac-ratio/#ftoc-heading-3" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">acquisition cost (CAC)</a> and repurchase rate. TrueProfit can support identifying your most valuable customers and implementing strategies to increase customer retention.</li> </ul> <div class="wrap-cta"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xs-12"> <p class="h2 acssd4c54">Track all your Profits &amp; Losses in real-time</p> <div class="content_cta"> <p>With TrueProfit, you get to know how much you’re truly making at any time.</p> <a href="https://apps.shopify.com/trueprofit?&amp;utm_source=trueprofit.io&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=ctabox&amp;utm_content=trueprofit-vs-beprofit" target="_blank" class="btn-cta">START FREE TRIAL</a> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xs-12"> <amp-img data-hero src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/TP.png" alt="" class="fullwwidth amp-wp-enforced-sizes" width="600" height="370" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="" class="fullwwidth amp-wp-enforced-sizes" width="600" height="370" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img> </div> </div> </div> <h4>BeProfit</h4> <p>As a top profit analytics app, BeProfit doesn’t fall behind TrueProfit in terms of tracking features and customizations:</p> <ul> <li><strong>Syncing capabilities:</strong> BeProfit can effortlessly sync your ad platforms, expenses, and order data. It also generates up-to-date reports that reflect the most recent information.</li> <li><strong>Custom reporting:</strong> Schedule custom reports and have them conveniently emailed directly to you. BeProfit will ensure that you stay informed and in control of your business’s financial performance.</li> <li><strong>Accessibility and collaboration:</strong> The app is accessible almost anywhere and anytime so that you can monitor your business, even on the go. Additionally, you can collaborate with your teammates, fostering seamless teamwork and shared insights.</li> <li><strong>Customer lifetime value analysis:</strong> Utilize cutting-edge cohort analysis provided by BeProfit to analyze important metrics, such as customer lifetime value, return on ad spend (ROAS), and customer acquisition cost (CAC). This feature is beneficial in the case of making data-driven decisions to optimize your business strategies.</li> <li><strong>UTM tracking:</strong> BeProfit offers UTM tracking capabilities, enabling you to optimize your advertising campaigns, email marketing, affiliate programs, and influencer collaborations. You will have access to a deeper understanding of their effectiveness and performance.</li> </ul> <h3><a href="https://getstartedtiktok.pxf.io/XYnvAM" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><amp-img data-hero class="aligncenter wp-image-3596 size-full amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2.png" alt="" width="728" height="90" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2.png 728w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2-300x37.png 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2-400x49.png 400w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="aligncenter wp-image-3596 size-full amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="" width="728" height="90" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2.png 728w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2-300x37.png 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/728x90_2-400x49.png 400w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img></a></h3> <h4>Final verdict</h4> <table class="table table-hover acsseb0ee"> <tbody> <tr> <td class="acss117a4">This is a close one.<strong> TrueProfit takes the lead with bundle analytics and custom expense tracking</strong>. <p>Both TrueProfit vs BeProfit are fantastic regarding what you can track, from your profits and losses of multiple stores, product analytics, customer analytics, and more. But TrueProfit gives you some extra tracking features:</p> <ul> <li>With TrueProfit, you can gain insights from your best-selling bundles– which you can use to increase your <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/average-order-value/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">AOV</a> with product bundles that are most likely to sell. BeProfit has product analytics, but the insights for which items sell well together are not available.</li> <li>Suppose you’re running an affiliate campaign; you can set custom affiliate cost = 10% revenue. This is yet to be possible with BeProfit.</li> </ul> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>#3. TrueProfit vs BeProfit: Ease of use</h3> <h4>TrueProfit</h4> <p>Ease of use is one of the notable features merchants love when talking about TrueProfit. With only 30 minute setup, you’ll gain access to your real-time profits and losses of multiple Shopify stores.</p> <p>TrueProfit synchronizes and puts all your data under stunning graphs and charts depicting your store’s key metrics. Plus, you can customize your report to view only the metrics that matter the most.</p> <figure id="attachment_3335" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3335 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-300x259.jpg" alt="TrueProfit’s modern and intuitive dashboard" width="1200" height="1038" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-300x259.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1024x885.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-768x664.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1536x1328.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-400x346.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-800x692.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1400x1210.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3335 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="TrueProfit’s modern and intuitive dashboard" width="1200" height="1038" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-300x259.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1024x885.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-768x664.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1536x1328.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-400x346.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-800x692.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use-1400x1210.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-trueprofit-ease-of-use.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>TrueProfit’s modern and intuitive dashboard</em></figcaption></figure> <h4>BeProfit</h4> <p>Likewise, BeProfit receives many positive reviews on the Shopify App Store with its ease of use, clean and visually appealing dashboard.</p> <p>When you install BeProfit, you’ll access an intuitive analytics dashboard and powerful profit tracking, allowing you to effortlessly calculate your profit, track costs, sync marketing spending, and view lifetime value reports.</p> <p>With this app, you can conveniently analyze your order metrics, shipping, inventory, marketing costs, attribution, and profits in one place. Whether you prefer automated or custom reports, BeProfit offers you the flexibility to generate the insights you need.</p> <figure id="attachment_3334" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3334 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-300x242.jpg" alt="BeProfit’s professional and well-categorized dashboard" width="1200" height="967" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-300x242.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1024x825.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-768x619.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1536x1238.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-400x322.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-800x645.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1400x1129.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3334 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="BeProfit’s professional and well-categorized dashboard" width="1200" height="967" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-300x242.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1024x825.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-768x619.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1536x1238.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-400x322.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-800x645.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use-1400x1129.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/3-beprofit-ease-of-use.jpg 1898w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>BeProfit’s professional and well-categorized dashboard</em></figcaption></figure> <h4>Final verdict</h4> <table class="table table-hover acsseb0ee"> <tbody> <tr> <td class="acss9b509"><strong>It’s a tie!</strong> Both TrueProfit and BeProfit are built with user experience in mind, allowing you to easily navigate around the app and keep track of all your key metrics without the sweating part. So, it’s a matter of your preference.</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h3>#4. TrueProfit vs BeProfit: Integration</h3> <h4>TrueProfit</h4> <p>TrueProfit seamlessly integrates with a range of platforms to provide you with comprehensive tracking and analysis capabilities. The app offers instant and real-time integration with popular ad channels such as Facebook, Google, Bing, Snapchat, and TikTok. This allows you to effortlessly sync and track your ad spends without manual data entry.</p> <figure id="attachment_3337" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3337 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-300x139.jpg" alt="TrueProfit’s seamless integrations" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3337 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="TrueProfit’s seamless integrations" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-trueprofit-integration.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>TrueProfit’s seamless integrations</em></figcaption></figure> <p>Additionally, TrueProfit integrates with various <a href="https://help.trueprofit.io/en/article/how-to-integrate-shipping-platforms-into-trueprofit-jgc9se/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">shipping platforms</a> (<em>Shippo, ShipStation, Shipwire, ShippingEasy, ShipBob, and Shiphero</em>), enabling you to factor in shipping costs accurately. The app also supports integration with other platforms, including marketing platforms, to gather and consolidate all relevant data for calculating your true profit.</p> <h4>BeProfit</h4> <p>BeProfit offers seamless integrations with various platforms, allowing you to streamline your business operations and gain accurate insights. The app integrates with your store platform, marketing channels, accounting software, payment processor, and shipping accounts.</p> <p>By syncing your ad platforms, expenses, and order data, BeProfit provides you with up-to-date reports that reflect the latest information.</p> <figure id="attachment_3336" class="thumbnail wp-caption aligncenter style="><amp-img data-hero class="wp-image-3336 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="http://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-300x139.jpg" alt="BeProfit’s extensive integrations with top ad channels and marketing platforms" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"><amp-img fallback data-hero class="wp-image-3336 amp-wp-enforced-sizes" src="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/plugins/accelerated-mobile-pages/images/SD-default-image.png" alt="BeProfit’s extensive integrations with top ad channels and marketing platforms" width="1200" height="558" srcset="https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-300x139.jpg 300w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1024x476.jpg 1024w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-768x357.jpg 768w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1536x714.jpg 1536w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-400x186.jpg 400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-800x372.jpg 800w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration-1400x650.jpg 1400w, https://trueprofit.io/wp-content/uploads/4-beprofit-integration.jpg 1920w" layout="intrinsic"></amp-img></amp-img><figcaption class="caption wp-caption-text"><em>BeProfit’s extensive integrations with top ad channels and marketing platforms</em></figcaption></figure> <p>With BeProfit’s integrations, you can analyze customer lifetime value, return on ad spend (ROAS), and customer acquisition cost (CAC) using cutting-edge cohort analysis.</p> <h4>Final verdict</h4> <table class="table table-hover acss6a996"> <tbody> <tr class="acssdca13"> <td class="acss00cf1">We would say <strong>this is a tie</strong>. Both apps allow you to integrate with your ad channels, shipping platforms, payment gateways, marketing tools, etc., without the hassle.</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h2>Round up: TrueProfit Offers Better Value For Your Money!</h2> <p>In conclusion, both TrueProfit vs BeProfit is powerful tools for tracking and analyzing your business’s profit and loss. While both apps offer a range of features and integrations, <strong>TrueProfit stands out as a more affordable option</strong>, particularly if you have thousands of orders per month.</p> <p>We hope this comparison of <strong>TrueProfit vs BeProfit</strong> has given you a clearer view of which is best for your business’s needs and wants. Stay true for more!</p> <p class="acss25665"><em>Discover what proper profit-tracking looks like at <a href="https://trueprofit.io/?utm_source=trueprofit.io&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=hyperlink&amp;utm_content=free-methods-to-track-your-shopify-profit" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-schema-attribute="">trueprofit.io</a></em></p> </div> <div class="amp-wp-content"><amp-addthis width="320" height="92" data-pub-id="ra-5cc8551aa4f16f5c" data-widget-id="cwgj"></amp-addthis></div>   <div class="amp-wp-content post-pagination-meta"> <div id="pagination"> <div class="next"> <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/click-through-rate/amp/">Click Through Rate (CTR): Defintion, Fomula and Calculator &raquo;</a> </div> <div class="prev"> <a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/ending-support-for-amazon/amp/"> &laquo; TrueProfit is Ending Support for Amazon Platform</a> </div> <div class="cb"></div> </div> </div>   </div> <div class="amp-wp-article-header amp-wp-article-category ampforwp-meta-taxonomy "> <div class="amp-wp-meta amp-wp-tax-category"> <span>Categories: </span> <span class="amp-cat-8"><a href="https://trueprofit.io/blog/category/ecommerce/amp/" title="eCommerce" > eCommerce</a></span> </div> </div> <div class="amp-wp-content amp_author_area ampforwp-meta-taxonomy"> <div class="amp_author_area_wrapper"> <amp-img src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b655b8a36f2fb21243314f6c1d7aaf95?s=70&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="70" height="70" layout="fixed"></amp-img> <strong> trueprofit</strong>: </div> </div> <div class="ampforwp-so-i"> <amp-social-share type="twitter" width="50" height="28" aria-label="twitter" data-param-url="" data-param-text="TITLE https://trueprofit.io/?p=3331 via " ></amp-social-share> <amp-social-share type="email" aria-label="email" width="50" height="28" ></amp-social-share> <amp-social-share type="pinterest" aria-label="pinterest" width="50" height="28" ></amp-social-share> <amp-social-share type="linkedin" aria-label="linkedin" width="50" height="28" ></amp-social-share> <a title="whatsapp share" href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=TrueProfit vs BeProfit: Which Is The Ultimate #1 Profit-Tracking Solution?&nbsp;https://trueprofit.io/blog/trueprofit-vs-beprofit/" aria-label="whatsapp share"> <div class="a-so-i"> <amp-img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8;base64," width="50" height="20" /> </div> </a> <a title="line share" href="http://line.me/R/msg/text/?https://trueprofit.io/blog/trueprofit-vs-beprofit/"> <div class="a-so-i custom-a-so-line" aria-label="line share"> <amp-img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8;base64," width="50" height="20" /> </div> </a> </div> <div id="comments" class="ampforwp-comment-wrapper"> <div class="cmt-button-wrapper"> </div> </div> </article> <footer class="amp-wp-footer"> <div id="footer"> <h2>TruePr